This project builds its own astrodynamics. At runtime it links only
permissively/MPL-licensed Rust crates (hifitime, ANISE — MPL-2.0;
nalgebra — Apache-2.0/MIT). Copyleft reference tools (REBOUND, ASSIST,
GRSS, nyx) are used exclusively offline to generate validation fixtures
and are never linked into or distributed with this software.
